1. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses the design of an intrusion detection system, which falls under the domain of cybersecurity. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on the design of a distributed IDS for local area networks, which is related to network architecture and design. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed IDS consists of a group of autonomous and cooperating agents, which suggests the use of AI techniques. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses the design of a distributed IDS, which falls under the domain of distributed computing. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper proposes a system design for an IDS, which is related to software engineering.
